<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Learn about Faithful Word and our mission to share God's truth.">
    <title>About | Faithful Word</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,400;1,500&family=Source+Sans+3:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main>
        <section class="about-hero">
            <div class="container container-narrow">
                <h1>About Faithful Word</h1>
                <p class="lead">A ministry dedicated to strengthening faith through Scripture-centered reflection and teaching.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="about-content">
            <div class="container container-narrow">
                <div class="about-section">
                    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                    <p>Faithful Word exists to encourage believers in their daily walk with Christ. We believe that God's Word is living and active, and through devotionals, testimonies, and Scripture studies, we seek to help others grow in their relationship with the Lord.</p>
                    <p>Whether you are new to faith or have walked with Christ for decades, our hope is that each article brings you closer to understanding God's infinite love and His purpose for your life.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="about-section">
                    <h2>What We Believe</h2>
                    <ul class="belief-list">
                        <li><strong>Scripture:</strong> We believe the Bible is the inspired, infallible Word of God and the ultimate authority for faith and life.</li>
                        <li><strong>The Gospel:</strong> We believe salvation comes through faith in Jesus Christ alone, by grace alone, for God's glory alone.</li>
                        <li><strong>Community:</strong> We believe the Church is the body of Christ, called to love, serve, and encourage one another.</li>
                        <li><strong>Discipleship:</strong> We believe every Christian is called to grow in Christlikeness and to share the Gospel with the world.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="about-section">
                    <h2>Our Heart</h2>
                    <blockquote class="about-verse">
                        <p>"But grow in the grace and knowledge of our Lord and Savior Jesus Christ. To him be glory both now and forever! Amen."</p>
                        <cite>2 Peter 3:18</cite>
                    </blockquote>
                    <p>This verse captures our heart. We want to see believers—including ourselves—continually growing in grace and knowledge. Not for our own sake, but so that Christ may be glorified in all things.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="about-section">
                    <h2>Get Involved</h2>
                    <p>Have a testimony to share? A devotional on your heart? A Scripture passage that changed your life? We invite you to contribute to Faithful Word and encourage others in the faith.</p>
                    <a href="/posts/new" class="btn btn-primary">Write an Article</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="scripture-banner">
            <div class="container">
                <blockquote>
                    <p>"Trust in the Lord with all your heart and lean not on your own understanding; in all your ways submit to him, and he will make your paths straight."</p>
                    <cite>Proverbs 3:5-6</cite>
                </blockquote>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
